  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK506">
<l>aṟṟārait tēṟuta lōmpuka maṟṟavar </l>
<l>paṟṟilar nāṇār paḻi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) avoid choosing men who have no relations; such men have no attachment, and thereforehave no fear of crime.</l>
            </lg>
